  "learningTips": [
    {
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Remember \"a acoperi\" sounds like \"a cover\" — both mean to put something over or prepare a surface."
    },
    {
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Think of \"cover\" as placing a cover on a table or bed, which helps you recall \"a acoperi\" easily."
    },
    {
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "The English word \"cover\" and Romanian \"acoperi\" share Latin roots, so they are related in meaning and sound."
    },
    {
      "lang": "en",
      "text": "Imagine setting the table by covering it with plates and cutlery — this visual links \"cover\" and \"a acoperi\"."
    }
